Warning [L0201]: implicit clone of `msg`; write `take msg` to transfer ownership or `.clone()` to silence this warning
  --> tests/ui_lint/implicit_clone.lex:7:13
    |
  7 |     consume(msg);
    |             ^^^
 Why: `consume` expects to take ownership of this value
 Fix: write `take msg` to move, or `msg .clone()` to copy explicitly
